to talk about.

38:45.250 --> 38:47.080
And that never set well with me,
which is how

38:47.080 --> 38:50.290
I ended up
in the principal's office.

38:50.290 --> 38:52.120
That kind of stigma
leaves us in the dark.

38:52.120 --> 38:55.830
Our medical needs
become this dirty secret.

38:55.830 --> 38:57.710
So when we need help,

38:57.710 --> 39:00.330
we often ourselves
struggling alone.

39:05.710 --> 39:07.790
But we're not alone.

39:07.790 --> 39:09.920
And that is why
it is so important

39:09.920 --> 39:14.210
